text: Rosport-Mompach () is a commune in Luxembourg. It is part of the canton of Echternach. It was created on 1 January 2018 from the former communes of Rosport and Mompach. As of 2019, 3,644 people live here. Category:2018 establishments in Luxembourg Category:Communes of Echternach
title: Rosport-Mompach
